          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-8055 ldev: Further improvements to ldev.",
        "message": "LU-8055 ldev: Further improvements to ldev.\n\nAllow for the hostname and backend file system to be used in command\nsubstitution. Output can now be filtered by using -R <role> or\n--role <role> as command line parameters, where role is a string such\nas \"mdt\", \"ost\", \"mgs\", or \"mgt\". All labels for a file system can be\nprinted by using the -F <name> or --filesys <name> as\ncommand line parameters, where name is the file system of interest.\n\nSigned-off-by: Giuseppe Di Natale <dinatale2@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: Icd02f7924380f483e927241a431e1c9645f480fe\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
